Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.76,0:05:19.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,ZERO對總領事下了Geass吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.61,0:05:20.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是為什麼
