Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.38,0:05:30.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真意外
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.49,0:05:31.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你竟獨自前來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.41,0:05:37.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中華聯邦的總領事應該已經承認日本合眾國了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.23,0:05:40.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那位大人即將去世
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.86,0:05:41.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還是說
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.94,0:05:44.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黑色騎士團要選擇在此毀滅一途嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.78,0:05:46.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,慢著 突然說這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.33,0:05:47.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.55,0:05:50.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就當總領事在我們手中光榮殉職好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.99,0:05:51.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,C.C.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.36,0:05:54.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,ZERO似乎點燃了意外的導火索啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.36,0:05:58.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是遠大的理想 還是庸俗的野心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.57,0:06:03.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姑且爭取到了讓羅洛等待的時間
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.07,0:06:08.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,若能得到C.C. 他就會隱瞞我恢復記憶的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.84,0:06:11.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然而 他的根本目的是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.12,0:06:15.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,似乎不是在布里塔尼亞陞遷或對其效忠
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.60,0:06:18.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這麼說 該尋找別的線索嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.32,0:06:22.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖是危險的牌 但有相應的價值
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.49,0:06:24.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒時間躊躇了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.48,0:06:27.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天籐堂他們就會被處刑
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.67,0:06:28.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.78,0:06:30.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的Geass已暴露給羅洛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.13,0:06:32.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算想辦法殺了羅洛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.06,0:06:35.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我記憶恢復的事也會被機情知道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.69,0:06:37.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣的話娜娜莉…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.89,0:06:40.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在救出娜娜莉之前
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.76,0:06:43.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有繼續假裝學生了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.54,0:06:47.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幸好 吉爾弗德等人似乎和機情聯繫不深
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.93,0:06:51.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,隱藏的Knightmare未被發現也能說明
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.25,0:06:53.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但僅此而已
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.94,0:06:54.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼才好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.69,0:06:57.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,救出黑色騎士團
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.67,0:07:00.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同時除去羅洛的方法…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.33,0:07:09.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難以接受
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.19,0:07:12.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是那小鬼殺了布魯諾嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.89,0:07:14.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是第五人了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.30,0:07:15.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,維克多也是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.26,0:07:17.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只不過碰到了他的掛墜盒就…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.11,0:07:19.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那人平時就有問題
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.33,0:07:20.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但也不至於被殺吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.50,0:07:26.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自稱ZERO的人都出現了 我們必須更團結
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.49,0:07:29.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟殺害同伴的死神 要怎麼組隊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.05,0:07:32.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,組隊？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.46,0:07:34.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,重點是任務吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.50,0:07:35.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要什麼同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.78,0:07:40.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,復活的ZERO是那個ZERO嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.89,0:07:41.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.14,0:07:45.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無論是哪個 都會再度拋棄我們吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.03,0:07:48.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總領事館的爆炸事件原因呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.69,0:07:50.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至今還沒有官方說明
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.78,0:07:53.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是有聯絡說認可執行處刑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.87,0:07:56.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,處刑不過是以儆傚尤
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.27,0:07:58.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以我來說是低級的手段
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.36,0:08:01.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,會出現嗎 ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.50,0:08:03.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不出來的話也好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.06,0:08:08.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無意引發奇跡的ZERO 也得不到民眾支持
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.72,0:08:10.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您連這一步都想到了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.77,0:08:13.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 我希望他出現
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.88,0:08:17.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 是祈禱他出現
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.57,0:08:20.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了不知身在何處的公主殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.89,0:08:25.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您為何承認日本合眾國
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.36,0:08:28.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還未向朱禁城確認就獨斷專行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.37,0:08:31.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即便是大宦官之一
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.45,0:08:33.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這行為也不可饒恕
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.61,0:08:36.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使您打算利用ZERO…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.61,0:08:39.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎可利用ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.15,0:08:40.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有ZERO才有幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.02,0:08:42.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聖上的聖意呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.55,0:08:44.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那種小丫頭哪比得上ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.69,0:08:48.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,ZERO會賜予我幸福才是絕對的法則
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.81,0:08:50.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這賣國賊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.49,0:08:55.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紅天已死
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.34,0:08:58.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.65,0:09:01.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無論殺害 情報操作還是偽裝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.89,0:09:03.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走哪條路羅洛都是瓶頸
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.26,0:09:07.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,處刑開始之前必須想辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.38,0:09:09.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到那情報的證據
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.29,0:09:19.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,過去曾自稱黑色騎士團
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.23,0:09:22.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,擾亂11區的恐怖分子的處刑
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.19,0:09:24.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在即將執行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.45,0:09:27.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,ZERO會現身於部下的刑場之上嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.11,0:09:29.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,ZERO大人 求求您
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.45,0:09:30.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,救救籐堂將軍
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.74,0:09:31.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別殺他們
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.33,0:09:41.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,ZERO背叛了我們
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.46,0:09:42.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他不會來救我們的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.99,0:09:44.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他一定會來的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.36,0:09:46.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要那是本人 只要他還活著
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.92,0:09:48.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定會來引發奇跡的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.82,0:09:50.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奇跡…嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.95,0:09:52.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別放鬆警戒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.68,0:09:54.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然可能性很低
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.08,0:09:55.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但C.C.也有可能出現
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.53,0:10:03.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,扇要…這下就結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.49,0:10:07.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出來吧 ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.01,0:10:11.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,父親安德列斯·達爾頓的仇…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.51,0:10:14.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大部隊發來機密指令
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.46,0:10:18.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為防止通信竊聽 命屬下口頭傳達
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.71,0:10:25.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的身份 我暫借一下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.43,0:10:31.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這該怎麼理解才好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.59,0:10:34.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,若ZERO出現 只管行動便是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.12,0:10:36.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算我們對布里塔尼亞開炮
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.95,0:10:38.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們也可以裝作一無所知？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.19,0:10:40.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想這交易不算壞
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.26,0:10:43.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽說你是武官
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.04,0:10:44.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看來搞政治也挺有一套啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.71,0:10:46.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,金梅爾卿
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.90,0:10:48.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先行量產機沒問題吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.23,0:10:52.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,機情使用過 說不定會有奇怪的壞習慣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.85,0:10:53.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是重要的機體
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.10,0:10:56.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有一點不對勁就立即報告
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.00,0:10:57.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡是金梅爾
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.49,0:11:00.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Vincent無異常 可以出擊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.59,0:11:03.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魯路修
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.86,0:11:06.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,若不遵守約定 就殺了你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.13,0:11:08.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉爾弗德卿
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.15,0:11:11.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 終於到了處刑時間
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.82,0:11:15.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黑色騎士團殘黨即將接受正義的制裁
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.10,0:11:15.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,ZERO大人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.07,0:11:16.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,求求您
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.20,0:11:18.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請顯示奇跡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.43,0:11:19.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,11區人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.90,0:11:23.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們所相信的ZERO沒有現身
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.84,0:11:25.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一切都是騙局
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.40,0:11:29.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他逃避了我提出的堂堂正正的決鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.35,0:11:30.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舉槍
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.33,0:11:37.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.51,0:11:38.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.43,0:11:39.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別動
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.46,0:11:41.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從這裡出去你也會被殺
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.42,0:11:42.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道 但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.74,0:11:43.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.06,0:11:46.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們已做得夠好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.44,0:11:47.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不對
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.48,0:11:50.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你錯了 吉爾弗德
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.90,0:11:52.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他來了 但是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.02,0:11:54.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們也無法出手
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.81,0:11:56.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼辦 憑你一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.13,0:11:57.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.50,0:12:00.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,繞到後面了嗎 ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.56,0:12:09.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉爾弗德 你即將處刑的不是恐怖分子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.15,0:12:12.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我合眾國軍 黑色騎士團的士兵
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.08,0:12:13.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是要我根據國際法
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.84,0:12:15.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,承認他們是俘虜？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.33,0:12:16.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.58,0:12:18.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然出現了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.81,0:12:21.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 若打破了與我的約定
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.18,0:12:22.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就要死 ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.74,0:12:26.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 魯路修·蘭佩洛奇
Comment: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,//---------------------------------TXTB------------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.22,0:12:36.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.17,0:12:38.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,ZERO現身了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.58,0:12:40.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多麼愚蠢的行為
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.39,0:12:41.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.46,0:12:42.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.57,0:12:43.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是本人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.90,0:12:46.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還用說嗎 ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.73,0:12:50.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然有公佈處刑的事 但沒有更多報導啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.47,0:12:51.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 但是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.83,0:12:52.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.64,0:12:53.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,ZERO只有一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.89,0:12:56.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然乘在Knightmare Frame上
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.36,0:12:58.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目的應該不是自首吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.25,0:13:00.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是若打算獨自一人作戰…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.19,0:13:01.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看 我說的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.19,0:13:05.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 就按去年的計劃行事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.95,0:13:09.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那得等ZERO先渡過這難關才行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.28,0:13:11.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笑世子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.16,0:13:15.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了今後的打算 先開始進行那個準備吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.41,0:13:17.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,布里塔尼亞軍方面已開始…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.90,0:13:18.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魯路修呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.01,0:13:20.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有羅洛跟著
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.46,0:13:22.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,半小時前就進了螺旋劇場
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.38,0:13:27.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,久違了 吉爾弗德卿
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.55,0:13:29.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出來敘敘舊如何
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.91,0:13:32.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,承蒙邀請 不過請容我謝絕
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.85,0:13:36.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,過去的因緣 讓我以Knightmare來回應吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.78,0:13:39.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不出來就無法使用Geass
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.20,0:13:41.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像你的風格
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.65,0:13:43.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼來確定規則吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.44,0:13:44.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,規則？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.37,0:13:45.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,決鬥的規則
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.68,0:13:49.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戰鬥要一對一做個了斷
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.62,0:13:52.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 我不會讓別人插手
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.87,0:13:54.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,武器只有一件
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.24,0:13:54.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.53,0:14:00.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的武器是這個
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.39,0:14:03.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 讓我借那面盾一用
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.36,0:14:04.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼 那是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.03,0:14:05.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這就行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.37,0:14:08.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鎮壓暴動用的盾
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.66,0:14:10.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,該不會 一開始就
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.49,0:14:11.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打算自我了斷嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.40,0:14:16.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真令人失望 ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.74,0:14:17.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.88,0:14:22.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能解決一隻寄生蟲大宦官 算是欠他個人情
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.42,0:14:26.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 這不是基於永續調和的盟約
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.48,0:14:27.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,若ZERO無能
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.06,0:14:31.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那只得讓黑色騎士團變成外交的工具了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.18,0:14:34.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,提個問題 吉爾弗德卿
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.44,0:14:37.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,若有正義無法擊敗的邪惡存在
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.79,0:14:39.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你會如何做
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.49,0:14:43.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不惜玷污雙手以惡制惡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.21,0:14:47.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還是寧可捨身取義 也要將自己的正義貫徹到底
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.78,0:14:49.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無論如何 留存下來的終究是邪惡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.00,0:14:52.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,矛盾 文字遊戲嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.56,0:14:55.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的正義與公主殿下同在
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.08,0:14:57.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.34,0:14:59.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,若是我 不惜化身為邪惡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.73,0:15:00.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也要擊殺極惡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.11,0:15:02.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,YES Your Highness
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.85,0:15:07.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.79,0:15:12.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,地震？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.73,0:15:14.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 這作戰是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.01,0:15:16.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黑色叛亂時的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.97,0:15:24.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第12步兵部隊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.62,0:15:26.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去第4等級的階層控制室
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.18,0:15:28.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,ZERO的部下…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.58,0:15:30.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡蓮
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.39,0:15:31.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你指揮突擊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.58,0:15:32.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.13,0:15:34.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自在戰鬥裝甲機部隊跟我來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.52,0:15:36.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,救出扇先生等人為最優先事項
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.90,0:15:41.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,α4呼叫α1 請回答 α1 α1
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.37,0:15:42.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡 有人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.18,0:15:45.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卑鄙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.63,0:15:51.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼一對一啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.72,0:15:55.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.61,0:15:58.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巴特
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.61,0:16:01.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黑色騎士團啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.10,0:16:03.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敵人已落入我國領土內
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.92,0:16:06.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快摧毀布里塔尼亞軍 拯救同胞
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.12,0:16:08.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同胞…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.84,0:16:11.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反過來利用了租界構造嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.68,0:16:14.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快 在布里塔尼亞重整態勢之前
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.32,0:16:15.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,解放所有人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.82,0:16:18.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,會被他們逃進中華聯邦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.29,0:16:21.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們的目的歸根到底是C.C.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.15,0:16:24.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這邊交給吉爾弗德
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.70,0:16:25.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這恐怖分子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.34,0:16:30.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,布里塔尼亞
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.50,0:16:33.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡已經是日本的領土了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.45,0:16:34.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日本是不存在的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.21,0:16:35.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.34,0:16:37.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以才討厭布里塔尼亞
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.47,0:16:42.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,永別了 11區的王牌
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.99,0:16:48.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,擋住了？在這個距離
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.93,0:16:51.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是輻射波動
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.64,0:16:54.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,近身後我的勝利就已成定局
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.47,0:16:56.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.82,0:17:05.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟敢把阿爾弗雷德
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.32,0:17:05.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別開槍
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.36,0:17:08.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡是中華聯邦的治外法權區
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.50,0:17:09.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.34,0:17:10.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有媒體的攝影機
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.46,0:17:13.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Vincent
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.88,0:17:15.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Vincent突擊了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.14,0:17:29.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這邊不能動 快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.82,0:17:32.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.86,0:17:34.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來了嗎 羅洛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.49,0:17:40.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然要逃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.30,0:17:42.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,交出C.C.的約定
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.63,0:17:45.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魯路修 一開始就欺騙了我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.89,0:17:49.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還不行 還不能被抓住
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.53,0:17:52.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明說要給我未來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.85,0:17:54.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能死在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.18,0:17:57.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要完成任務 就有未來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.25,0:18:04.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.25,0:18:06.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,物理現象停止不了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.90,0:18:09.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直接命中線路
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.02,0:18:11.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟在這種地方…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.11,0:18:18.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手 戴維德
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.30,0:18:21.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,若打中總領事館 就要跟中華聯邦開戰了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.41,0:18:22.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.32,0:18:24.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.27,0:18:30.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼 要救我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.62,0:18:32.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為 你是我弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.15,0:18:36.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使是被移植的記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.65,0:18:39.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和你共同度過的那段時間 並無虛假
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.95,0:18:43.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至今為止的生活 不是虛假
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.76,0:18:46.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為你是我弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.34,0:18:48.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.73,0:18:50.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.84,0:18:55.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那一天 沒有生日的我第一次
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.57,0:18:56.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,收到那個
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.12,0:19:00.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明說了 自己的性命最重要
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.84,0:19:02.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卻為了那種無聊的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.87,0:19:04.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為約好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.00,0:19:06.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的嶄新未來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.86,0:19:10.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的未來 和我…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.82,0:19:13.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,ZERO 在此了斷吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.18,0:19:15.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃我一擊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.78,0:19:18.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以這鐵錘
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.03,0:19:26.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.85,0:19:28.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼意思 金梅爾卿
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.80,0:19:29.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.98,0:19:31.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道 你是ZERO的同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.15,0:19:33.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是 我是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.88,0:19:35.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魯路修死了任務就…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.54,0:19:36.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 但是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.83,0:19:38.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.88,0:19:43.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.98,0:19:44.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,羅洛 糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.96,0:19:45.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是維蕾塔老師打來的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.68,0:19:47.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用IMOpen（即時通信公開線路）連接
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.52,0:19:50.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,羅洛嗎 你去哪兒了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.16,0:19:51.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.22,0:19:53.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,討厭啦 老師
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.93,0:19:55.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上個廁所好歹讓我們分別解決啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.57,0:19:58.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對了 剛才怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.03,0:20:00.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總領事館的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.02,0:20:03.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 好像很轟動啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.80,0:20:06.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟糕 若之前的事被知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.60,0:20:07.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就會被機情局處決
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.28,0:20:09.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個人也…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.15,0:20:11.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.95,0:20:14.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不會再讓弟弟捲進危險的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.11,0:20:16.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這不是當然的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.88,0:20:19.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,羅洛不適合殺人的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.13,0:20:24.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到此為止 布里塔尼亞的各位
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.25,0:20:27.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,更進一步的行動將視為武力介入
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.36,0:20:28.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,撤退吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.64,0:20:35.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.22,0:20:37.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,扇先生
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.04,0:20:39.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝 卡蓮
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.87,0:20:43.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,籐堂先生你們也…太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.28,0:20:45.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 給你添麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.67,0:20:46.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,受苦了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.99,0:20:48.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們也是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.25,0:20:50.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那台Knightmare呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.07,0:20:55.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道 那架機體本是敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.34,0:20:57.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在的機師我也…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.58,0:20:59.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他保護了ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.40,0:21:01.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至少不是敵人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.05,0:21:05.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明C.C.就在眼前 我卻…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.81,0:21:09.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一開始 在布里塔尼亞就沒有安寧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.82,0:21:11.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的歸宿 在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.44,0:21:16.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,落網了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.94,0:21:19.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然把這種資料留在司令室
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.99,0:21:22.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說明除了Geass以外一無所長吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.65,0:21:24.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這玩意裡的密碼竟能派上用場
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.17,0:21:26.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.01,0:21:28.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,模式D
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.44,0:21:31.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對了 ZERO的機體取這個軌道時
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.03,0:21:34.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從後方攻擊追逐他的Knightmare
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.46,0:21:36.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後若ZERO逃出
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.58,0:21:38.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就把對方的Knightmare完全破壞
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.15,0:21:41.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不逃出的話 就原地待機
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.15,0:21:44.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.46,0:21:51.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,將娜娜莉取而代之的冒牌貨
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.42,0:21:53.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看我搾乾你的每一滴血
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.42,0:21:55.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再像破抹布一樣拋棄
Comment: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,//---------------------------------NEXT------------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.04,0:23:41.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼羅洛·蘭佩洛奇
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.67,0:23:43.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要把那傢伙當我弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.74,0:23:45.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,簡直令人恥辱到渾身發抖
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.66,0:23:49.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很遺憾 若你忠實於機情的任務
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.20,0:23:51.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就能在那時被狙擊而亡了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.77,0:23:54.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哼 只要今後你能成為方便的棋子
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.97,0:23:56.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再在身邊留一陣也罷
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.00,0:24:00.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但別忘了 你只是頂替娜娜莉的冒牌貨
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.99,0:24:03.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在被用在最佳局面那一天之前
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.42,0:24:05.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就盡情享受一下片刻的兄弟遊戲吧
